'''Egypt''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its three default cities are the capital, Cairo, along with Giza and Luxor.

==Information==
Being an Islam-based country, female characters in BitLife will wear hijabs when they are adults. This is shared with females in [[Iran]], [[Iraq]], [[Afghanistan]], or [[Saudi Arabia]]. However unlike [[Afghanistan]], [[Iran]], [[Iraq]], [[Saudi Arabia]], or [[United Arab Emirates|UAE]], females do not have hijabs in Egypt.

